{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "15.0",
      "line_index": 15,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ed95ba56",
      "speaker": "アポロの声",
      "ja": "……スキャン結果を端末に送信しました。ルート通りに進めば、都度修正して水源へと辿り着けるでしょう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "17.1",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1c6cb208",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "登録完了。これで砂漠で迷う心配はありませんね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "19.1",
      "line_index": 19,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a266d1a3",
      "speaker": "ライラ",
      "ja": "準備は出来たの？それじゃあ出発ね！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.1",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "663dd56",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "え、貴方もついてくるの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.1",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6f2c9688",
      "speaker": "ライラ",
      "ja": "勿論！　私だけ待ってるなんて出来ないわ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.1",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "666c8784",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "（待っていてくれたほうがありがたいんですけどね……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.1",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f05cef89",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "……でも、砂漠に詳しい人が１人はいたほうがいいかも？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "29.1",
      "line_index": 29,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "94e6fb87",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "仕方有りませんね。では向かうとしましょう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "31.1",
      "line_index": 31,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6e3bff2a",
      "speaker": "ライラ",
      "ja": "改めて、出発ー！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2cfb35e0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ……暑い……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.0",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1ce1e72",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ジリジリと射す日光に炙られ、額をつたう汗が鼻に溜まって滴り落ちる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.0",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "23042da6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ルミナ、大丈夫か……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "55.1",
      "line_index": 55,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c3a6477a",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "うん……{G_PlayerName}くんこそ、大丈夫……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.0",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c98e5e76",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "日除けのフードは貰ったからな。……本当なら男として、譲りたいんだけど",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "59.1",
      "line_index": 59,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "32bcfa81",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "遠慮、しないで……この服、体温調節機能があるし……リリアンだから、{G_PlayerName}くんより丈夫だよ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.0",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a007c1cb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "でも、ルミナは……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.1",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c3a90a1c",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "病弱、と思うかも知れないけど……能力を使わなかったら平気だから……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.0",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "aa1a9609",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（本当なのかな……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "77.1",
      "line_index": 77,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6147f763",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あ、見て！　あそこ、植物があるわよ！　すごいゴツゴツしてる……アレって何なの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.1",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "446b03b7",
      "speaker": "ライラ",
      "ja": "え？　あれは、おうき……街でも見たことがないわね。初めて見たわ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.1",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2ce9f735",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そうなの。砂漠って変な植物とか動物が多いって聞いたけど、種類も多いのね？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.1",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "59a8886d",
      "speaker": "ライラ",
      "ja": "そうね、特に毒がある生き物には注意しないと……しかし、砂の上って、結構歩くと疲れるのね……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.1",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f042d660",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "え？　も、もしかして……歩き慣れてないの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.1",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "603ff7dc",
      "speaker": "ライラ",
      "ja": "い、今まで機会が無かっただけよ！　……大抵、ラクダ車を使ってたし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.1",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "965fcf18",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "この国に住んでて、砂の上を歩かない事なんてあるの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.1",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f64542d7",
      "speaker": "ライラ",
      "ja": "こ、こんな距離歩くの初めてってだけだもん！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.0",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7eeb296d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（本当にあの国の人なのかな……？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "97.1",
      "line_index": 97,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c773a916",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "（どーしましょ、もし病人でずっと部屋にいた子とかだったら……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.1",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d1888639",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ルートが更新されました。……おおよそ同じ方角ですが、若干西寄りですね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.1",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1e3bc9c0",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "ふふ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.1",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5c8a0166",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "どうされましたか、ルミナ様？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "114.1",
      "line_index": 114,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "61ab222b",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "ううん。なんだか……雫の案内で進んでると、一緒に旅が出来てるんだなって……思って。いいなって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.1",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6ca36a7a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "る、るみなしゃま……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.1",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "eac6ee26",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "わたくしが汗で汚れていなければ、間違いなく抱きしめていたのに……！　ああ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.1",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2f8f69fa",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "……汚れてなくても、暑いからイヤ……かな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "127.1",
      "line_index": 127,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2c4d6e8",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "…………！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.0",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b8ce8dcd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "雫が急に姿勢を低くし、進行方向とは違う方角を見つめる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.1",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ef75d5ba",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "……どうか、したの……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.1",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7088f66b",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "……皆様、何かが遠くから来ます！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.0",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "aeb1c55f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "雫の声を聞き、砂の海の向こう側へ目を凝らす。……確かに凄いスピードで、こちらに近づいてくる影があった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "155.1",
      "line_index": 155,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ac35953f",
      "speaker": "ライラ",
      "ja": "あれは……もしかして砂賊！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.0",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c182dba1",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "砂賊……って、ライラが言ってた……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "159.1",
      "line_index": 159,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "122b9698",
      "speaker": "ライラ",
      "ja": "どこの国にも属してない、ゴロツキの集まりよ！　……まだ大して国から離れてないのに、こんなところで会うなんて！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "172.0",
      "line_index": 172,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d7f40871",
      "speaker": "？？？",
      "ja": "………………",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
